metadata.name: DEJITARU PĀRU NFT #1
metadata.description: The DEJITARU PĀRU NFT project features unique and intricate digital collectibles created using artificial intelligence. It has a dedicated community of strong holders and constantly evolves with new, one-of-a-kind designs. These NFTs depict dragons and pearls in intricate detail, each being entirely unique and impossible to replicate. Each NFT grants access to an exclusive DAO community, voting rights over the DAO's assets, and passive income generated from the pearl.
